Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 那把短剑是谁的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose dagger was it, Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥 他被索隆的仆从杀害了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother. He was killed by servants of Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔苟斯战败后 你们称之为索隆的那一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After Morgoth's defeat, the one you call Sauron,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图打造一种力量 并非来源于肉体 而是让肉体受控于它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he sought to craft a power not of the flesh, but over flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I killed Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}á kuita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪莉 快回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Dilly, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但尽管我们竭尽全力 枯萎还是加速了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But despite our every effort, our decline has only quickened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘银…是我们唯一的救赎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This mithril... It is our only salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事物都无法削弱它的光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing diminishes its light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-都林国王… -够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-King Durin... -Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不会拿矮人们的生命冒险 去帮助精灵逃避死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not risk Dwarven lives to help the Elves cheat death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里等待你的将是黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All that awaits you there is darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Adar! Adar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开这片大陆吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let us put this land behind our sails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-与你并肩作战 我感觉… -我也感觉到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fighting at your side, I felt... -I felt it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个伤口需要精灵族的药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wound needs Elvish medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐国王以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strength to the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-警告他将要发生的事情 -独自前往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Warn him what's comin'. -Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会独行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大绿林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not a peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们前来为您效劳 索隆大君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We come to serve you, Lord Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指环王：力量之戒\N第一季第八集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔加拉德明天到达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gil-galad arrives tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我们汇报 能够拯救所有精灵王国的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}expecting to be presented with a means of saving all Elvendom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们却一筹莫展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we have none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有某种方式…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If only there was some way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够事半功倍就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of doing more with less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳刚诞生的时候 还没有我的巴掌大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Sun itself began as something no bigger than the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量 怎么能与太阳的创造者相提并论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how could we possibly match the powers that wrought the Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没时间了 凯勒布林博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're out of time, Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须告知至高王我们失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must inform the High King of our failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来精灵必须 做好准备 永久放弃这片海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then the Elves must prepare to abandon these shores. Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六天前 他被敌人的长矛刺中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Enemy lance. Six days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马不停蹄地赶了过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We rode without rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能救救他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}á tul? koivienna...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方大地的国王  你怎么会和他有交集呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}King of the Southlands? How is it your path crossed with his?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is it you are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is it you are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我们有很多事情要谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come. We have much to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当初就不应该让你上那艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have set you on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本应该相信你的 这种错误我以后不会再犯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have trusted you. It is a mistake I will not make again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从那艘船上跳下来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I leapt from that ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我深知自己还不配重返维林诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I believed in my heart I was not yet worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道 不知何故 自己在这里的任务还没有完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew that, somehow, my task here was not yet complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我浮出水面时 我能做的只有拼命游泳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when I surfaced, all I could do was swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并祈祷自己做了明智之选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and pray I had chosen wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当初游过那片苦海…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not cross that bitter ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是为了现在功败垂成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only to drown now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不能让你失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nor will I let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下来怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are we to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做我们唯一能做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only thing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劲地游\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在那儿 出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's there? Reveal yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔在这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Galadriel here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在休息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't you be resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里曾是凯勒布林博的工作间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was the workshop of Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位凯勒布林博吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Celebrimbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会在这里吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He's not here, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…其实 他就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... As a matter of fact, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯勒布林博…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我师从的那位大师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The master I apprenticed to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前经常说起你无与伦比的手艺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}used to speak of the wonders of your craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我未曾想过自己能有机会亲眼所见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never dreamed that I'd ever get the chance to see them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是铁匠吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you a smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我跟您可没法相提并论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... Nothing like your artistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些宝石 我从未见过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These gemstones, I've never seen anything like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用它们做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you plan to use them for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费艾诺的珠宝工艺 成功地捕捉到了维林诺的圣光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}F?anor's jewelcraft managed to capture the essence of Valinor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能在中洲如法炮制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had hoped to do the same for Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种矿石很奇特 它是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a peculiar ore. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请还给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有试过将它 和其他矿石结合 更好地发挥潜能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you tried combining it with other ores? To better stretch it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种矿石不适合这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That wouldn't be suitable for this ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-为什么不行  -因为所需数量庞大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why not? -Because in the amounts we need,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会大幅稀释其独一无二的品质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would too greatly dilute its unique qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的问题可能会有点蠢 请见谅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, but, uh, at the risk of sounding a fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰当的合金组合 难道不是能强化这些品质吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}couldn't the right alloy also amplify those qualities?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... Amplify?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我练手艺的地方 贵重金属简直是凤毛麟角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where I came up, precious metals were scarce as hens' teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们学会了 将各种金属结合 从而扬长避短\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-So we learnt to combine them to harness strengths and hide flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾见过在铁中 添加微量的镍 使刀锋更轻 更坚固\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen a trace of nickel added to iron to make a blade lighter and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的这种矿石 难道没有合金能强化它的品质吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Might there not be some alloy to amplify the qualities of your ore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个建议有点意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that is... an intriguing suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称之为…天赋吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Call it... a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 他将踏上 那条所有人都会踏上的归途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, he will travel that road which makes an end of every man who walks it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港口将会一片悲恸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Black flags will fill our harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有责任为他建造一座坟墓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be our duty to forge for him a tomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用石头赋予他不朽之身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}granting him the immortality in stone that no man,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种不朽 任何人 任何国王都无法获得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not even a king, can attain in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经召集了努门诺尔 各地的绘图员前来描绘国王的容貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Draftsmen from across Númenor have been summoned to capture his visage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让他们给出一个图样方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so they can propose a design.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在所有的学徒之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of all the apprentices,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要提出一项图样方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you have been chosen to propose one as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接下来的日子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the coming days,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们每个人 都将获准与国王相处一小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}each of you will be granted one hour with the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好利用这段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道黑夜里你一直在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what you have been doing in the dark of night
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你以为大家都睡着了 -对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-when you thought all eyes were asleep. -I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的侍女马上就会回来 国王大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your handmaid will be back in a moment, my king.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么还有时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then there is still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有时间干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时间警告你 年轻的弥瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To warn you, young Míriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您搞错了 我不是… -还不是女王吗 没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You're mistaken. I'm not... -Queen yet? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你会成为女王的 所以听好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you will be. So know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能尽快恢复 我们与精灵族往日的交好与联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if the old ways of our people are not soon restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的岛屿将会陷落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our island will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国王 救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the king! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧 你必须得走上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come. You must go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别像我那样找寻了太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't do as I did. I looked for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我已分不清现在与过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, I cannot separate what is from what was,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也分不清过去与未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what was from what will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个中洲 仰赖一物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One object. For all Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 我知道这听起来很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it sounds strange, High King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可以肯定 我们穷尽了所有可能的解决方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But surely, we should exhaust every possible solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么样的物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Precisely what manner of object?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会比之前想象的要小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be smaller than previously imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以随身携带的物品…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something that could be carried...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一把权杖 -一把剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-A scepter perhaps. -A sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是…一顶王冠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or perhaps... A crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是王冠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why a crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环形会是理想之选\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A circular form will be ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完整的环状物中 光线能在弧形里折射回自身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Allowing the light to arc back upon itself in one unbroken round,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打造出一种近乎无限的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}building to a power that is all but unbounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你要把这所有力量 都集中在一个精灵的头顶之上吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you would place all that power upon the brow of one being?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是随便哪个精灵 而是您啊至高王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not just any one being, High King. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些悄声暗示危险得很…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perilous are these whisperings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的时候 危险的那条道路才是唯一的出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes the perilous path is the only path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我也不会站在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't be standing here otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来就不应该在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should not be standing here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 我们只求给够时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High King, we ask only for the time needed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集精灵巧匠 测试凯勒布林博的理论…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to gather the Elven-smiths and test Celebrimbor's theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our time runs short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没错 所以… -时间比你们了解的还要紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yes, that is why... -Shorter than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从南方大地的火山爆发后 大树的枝叶就开始疯狂掉落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since the mountain of fire's eruption, the Great Tree is all but bleeding leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 最后一片树叶也将凋落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, the last will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我们的人民 离开这片海岸 否则我们也将衰亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And unless our people leave these shores, so shall we.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中洲没有哪个精灵 比我更迫切想要找出解决方案了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no Elf in Middle-earth who wanted a solution more than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果这真能拯救我们 恐怕还得再快一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if this was to be our salvation, I'm afraid we needed it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来差点就完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I almost had it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过因为 和那个来自南方大地的人说话…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was only in speaking with the Southlander that I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个下等人 这个主意是他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The low man? This idea was his?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是他的建议 才让我想出了这个解决方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His suggestions were but the key that unlocked the dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们眼看着就要打造出一股新的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are on the cusp of crafting a new kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是物理力量 而是精神力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not of strength, but of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非来源于肉体 而是让肉体受控于它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not of the flesh, but over flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可见世界的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a power of the Unseen World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 领主凯勒布林博\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry, Lord Celebrimbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此命令你解散这座城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are hereby commanded to disband the city
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并立即返回林顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and return to Lindon immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家都是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句话 “控制肉体的力量”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those words, "a power over flesh."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪里听到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did you hear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才在和巧匠们商议 我觉得…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was conferring with my smiths. I think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那句是我的原话 -哈尔布兰德刚才和你在一起吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I believe those are my words. -Was Halbrand with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要吗 反正已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does it matter? It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至高王 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High King, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉… -给我三个月时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I am sorry... -Grant me three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你欠我三个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am owed that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不欠你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are owed nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别为了补偿我而答应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then do it not out of recompense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在我求您的份上 答应我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do it because I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是虚假的希望 埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a fool's hope, Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已 再无更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Merely that. Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“希望从来都不是 微不足道的 即便希望很渺茫”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Hope is never mere. Not even when it is meager."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你已经忘了自己的忠告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or have you forgotten your own counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找皇室血脉的记录 要找出与南方大地有关的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need royal lineages, bloodlines. Anything you can find on the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对凡人王国的记录有限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our records are limited concerning the mortal kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些信息我得去地下墓穴里找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll have to scour the catacombs for that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-躲起来 -三个星期…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come. -Three weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这工作耗时三个世纪 却只给我三个星期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three weeks for a labor that could take three centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧迫的时间就是发明的动力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Constraint can be the very progenitor of invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 别对任何人提起此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Speak of this to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯勒布林博会找到办法的 我很确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor will find a way. I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然之间你们俩彼此这么熟悉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of a sudden, the two of you seem quite familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是尽己所能 提供一些微不足道的帮助而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just offering whatever humble aid I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我还是不敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To tell you the truth, I can still hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的人居然能在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone like me, here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与埃瑞吉安的精灵巧匠共事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}working with the Elven-smiths of Eregion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢我把你带来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For bringing you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也救过我 我们互不相欠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you saved mine. Our scales are balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你为我做的远不止这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you've done far more than that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点就放弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd all but given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你选择了相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you, you believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我身上看到了力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saw strength in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我拔高到了 其他人无法帮我实现的高度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You pushed me to heights that no one else could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点我永远不会忘却\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会确保其他人也永远铭记\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll see to it that no one else does either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 别害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not be afraid, master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的力量越觉醒 迷雾就会越弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The more your powers awaken, the more the veil will weaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷雾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Veil?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些打败您的人 在您的脑海中设下的障碍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The one placed upon your mind by those who cast you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们前来就是为了欢迎您的回归\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we have come here to welcome you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将您接回我们的领土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To bring you to our lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的领土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your lands?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您其实已经知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know them already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些星星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫做隐士之帽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is called the Hermit's Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在一个地方能看到这个星座图案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A pattern visible in but one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远的东方 那里的星座图案很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Far to the east, where the stars are strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁恩之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lands of Rh?n.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-鲁恩… -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Rh?n... -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的真实身份 最终将在那里为众人所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where you will be known at last, for who you truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您从星空坠入凡间 但却比星星更加伟大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fell from the stars, yet you are greater than they.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为火会服从您的意志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For fire obeys your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您倒在凡尘之下 而凡尘却惧怕于您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fell below the dust, yet dust fears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您若发怒 凡尘皆颤抖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For it trembles when you are wroth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风和水 冷与热\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The winds and waters, the heat and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.37,0:22:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您将在鲁恩学会控制所有这些力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Rh?n, you shall learn to command them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个行走或爬行的生物 都将成为您的奴隶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And every being that walks or crawls shall be your slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-因为您是索隆大君 -因为您是索隆大君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you are Lord Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:22:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假以时日 他将学会控制自己的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In time, he will learn to control his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在 暂时先把他绑起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For now, bind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确实有出馊主意的“优良”传统 但这回恐怕是最馊的一次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, in the grand tradition of bad ideas, this might well be the worst yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你有更好的想法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, have you got a better notion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三个居住者不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Third one's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd the third one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个总比三个强 现在就是我们的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better two than three. Now's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.62,0:24:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白兰地足 快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brandyfoot! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.83,0:25:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 冷静下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Master, calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.70,0:26:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nori. Nori, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.04,0:26:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.16,0:27:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他睁开眼看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make him see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.50,0:28:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.70,0:28:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你 求你了 拿着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need you. Please, just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.58,0:28:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我远点 否则我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get away from me. Or I wi...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.95,0:28:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再次伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will hurt you. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.75,0:28:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 他们对你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? What have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.91,0:28:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们向我展示了我的真实身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They showed me what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.91,0:28:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份只有你自己才能决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only you can show what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.08,0:29:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行为决定了你的善恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You choose by what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.20,0:29:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来帮忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.66,0:29:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.91,0:29:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睛闭上 只会疼一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close your eyes. -It'll only hurt but a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.41,0:29:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.95,0:30:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从黑影中来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From shadow you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.83,0:30:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令你们滚回黑影中去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To shadow I bid you return!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.12,0:30:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他不是索隆 -他是另外一个 是那个伊斯塔尔…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-He is not Sauron. -He is the other. The Istar. He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.70,0:30:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.04,0:31:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.29,0:31:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨道克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sadoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.66,0:31:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动 我们会想办法把你带回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold still. We'll find a way to carry you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.79,0:31:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 好姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, good lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.62,0:31:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我就要偏离轨道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid I'm about to go a' wandering off-trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.70,0:31:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布罗斯先生…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Burrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.16,0:31:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 普罗德菲洛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right, Proudfellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.29,0:31:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人肯定会在那边等着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The missus will be waitin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.62,0:31:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意 我现在只想坐一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if you don't mind, I'd just like to sit a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着看太阳升起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watch the Sun come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.45,0:33:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, two, three,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.16,0:33:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四 五 六\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-four, five, six,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.29,0:33:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七 八…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}seven, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.16,0:33:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共是九步…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.70,0:33:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到主杆一共九级台阶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stairs to main-post.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.00,0:33:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您做得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.33,0:33:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 你敢再这样怜悯我 我就降你的职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Patronize me like that again, Captain, I'll have your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.87,0:33:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.54,0:33:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我护着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.62,0:33:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那谁来护着你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who has you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.33,0:34:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉴于你的丧子之痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Given your loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.79,0:34:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去后 如果你想请辞 我非常理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would understand it if upon our return, you wish to take a leave of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.91,0:34:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有一次问我 为什么要把加拉德瑞尔从海里救出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You once asked me why I pulled Galadriel from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.25,0:34:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自称当时别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I claimed to have had little choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.87,0:34:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实是 我本可以把她留在海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the truth is, I could have left her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.16,0:34:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本可以拒绝随她到中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could've refused to follow her to Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.58,0:34:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者阻止我儿子去中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or stopped my son from doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.75,0:34:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在每一个转折点 我都做出了当下的选择 因为…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet at every turn, I made the choices I did because...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.37,0:34:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 埃兰迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why, Elendil?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.45,0:34:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为“埃兰迪尔” 不光意味着“爱星星的人”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because "Elendil" does not merely mean "one who loves the stars."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.75,0:34:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是没想到会导致现在这种结局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just never imagined it would lead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.08,0:35:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲曾经告诉我 忠贞派的处事方式就是要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father once told me that the way of The Faithful
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.16,0:35:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衷心实意付出代价…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is committing to pay the price...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.91,0:35:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便还不知道代价会是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if the cost cannot be known.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.58,0:35:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要相信 付出的代价终将会是值得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And trusting that, in the end, it will be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.79,0:35:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候代价会很高昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes the cost is dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.00,0:35:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.75,0:35:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们别无选择 只能继续履职尽责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have little choice then but to keep serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.25,0:35:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我敢说 我会让结局对得起这份代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I, for one, will see to it that we make the end worth the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.79,0:35:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come what may?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.41,0:35:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come what may.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.50,0:36:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 能看见努门诺尔了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain. Númenor is in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.79,0:36:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.04,0:36:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃兰迪尔 怎么了 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elendil, what is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.95,0:36:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.70,0:36:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.29,0:37:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.58,0:37:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘银太孤傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The mithril is proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.75,0:37:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它拒绝与次等矿石结合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It refuses every effort to bond it with lesser ores.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.83,0:38:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汲取物质世界和不可见世界的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tapping into the powers of the Seen and Unseen World
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.58,0:38:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎弱化了两者之间的界限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}seemed to soften the boundaries between the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.41,0:38:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本讲不通啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.66,0:38:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们施加的压力 大到能让天地都融为一体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We used enough pressure to fuse the heavens with earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.45,0:38:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这次本来应该行啊  -要有耐心 这是一个过程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-It should have held this time! -Patience. This is a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.79,0:38:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非每次努力 都是朝着进步的方向 这需要时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not every step we take will be forward. It may take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.75,0:38:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-时间 我们没有时间 -时间…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Time? We don't... We don't have time. -Time...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.70,0:38:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不今天就到这里吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps that is enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.08,0:38:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我们把自己逼得太紧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we've been pushing ourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.12,0:38:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我们把自己逼得太紧了”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Pushing ourselves too hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.29,0:38:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如说这就是问题所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposing that's the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.54,0:38:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如说是我们用力过猛呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Supposing we've been using too much force?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.37,0:38:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.50,0:38:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是不应该强迫金属的结合…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meaning that the metals shouldn't be forced to join...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.75,0:38:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是应该将彼此吸引 诱导到一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But more drawn or coaxed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.75,0:38:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是这样 那我们一直在朝反方向努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if that's true, we've been... we've been doing it all inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.04,0:38:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把它拆开 我们重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quickly. Dismantle this. We start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.62,0:39:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.95,0:39:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找到方法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道以前怎么没发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how we missed it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.41,0:39:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的力量过于强大 单个物体无法承受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's too much power for one object.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.29,0:39:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要两个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need two.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.66,0:39:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要做两个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're making two.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.95,0:39:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-两个王冠  -不完全是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Two crowns? -Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.62,0:39:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得做成稍微…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll need to be something...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.66,0:39:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小一点的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.54,0:39:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你自己看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come, see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.75,0:39:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先告诉我你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not until you tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.87,0:39:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.54,0:39:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说你真正的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.54,0:40:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 恐怕我听不…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel, I'm afraid I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.87,0:40:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有南方大地的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no King of the Southlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.00,0:40:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条血脉早就断掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The line was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.50,0:40:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上的徽章 它最后的主人 早在一千多年前就去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last man to bear your crest died over a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.29,0:40:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他没有继承人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had no heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.00,0:40:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你 我是在死人身上找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I found it on a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.66,0:40:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.58,0:40:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 在木筏上 你救了我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, on the raft, you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.66,0:40:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在木筏上 是你救了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the raft, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.50,0:40:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说服了弥瑞尔出兵拯救中洲的人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You convinced Míriel to save the Men of Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.41,0:40:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说服了她 我当时可是想留在努门诺尔的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You convinced her. I wanted to remain in Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.54,0:40:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你与我并肩作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fought beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.75,0:40:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗击你的敌人 以及我的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Against your enemy. And mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.70,0:40:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.87,0:41:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自打创始之初 我就已经醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been awake since before the breaking of the first silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.58,0:41:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…我有很多个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In that time... I have had many names.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.33,0:41:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没站稳当吧 妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lose your footing again, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.79,0:41:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是摔了一下而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was just a little tumble, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.00,0:41:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your feet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.16,0:42:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚出我的大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 妹妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.41,0:42:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.20,0:42:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.41,0:42:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的旧短剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My old dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.62,0:42:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间你一直好好保管着它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've kept it safe all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.83,0:42:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直很勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have been very brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.41,0:42:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你苦苦战斗了这么多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have fought so hard. For so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.70,0:42:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去完成我的未竟之事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To complete the task that I could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.37,0:42:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是猎杀索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your task was hunting Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.20,0:42:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务是确保和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My task was to ensure peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.91,0:42:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我了解到 索隆的任务也是确保和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I learned that was Sauron's task as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.16,0:43:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.87,0:43:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.16,0:43:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为索隆 你和无数精灵一起牺牲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Along with countless others, because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.83,0:43:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.75,0:43:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他寻求力量并不是为了摧毁中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was seeking a power not to destroy Middle-earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.00,0:43:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是将其治愈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but to heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.50,0:43:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的精灵同胞们 正在力求做到的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as your fellow Elves are seeking to do this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.41,0:43:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必对他们撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You needn't lie to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.37,0:43:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只消让工作继续进行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Simply let the work proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.66,0:43:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得就在这棵树下 我对你耳语的那番话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember what I whispered to you under this very tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.87,0:43:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再触碰一次黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Touch the darkness once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.50,0:44:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥死了 全都是因为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My brother is dead. Because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.58,0:44:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 你为什么要说这种话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.20,0:44:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说这样的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.25,0:44:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.29,0:44:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 回到我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.83,0:44:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.16,0:44:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.87,0:44:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.62,0:44:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.79,0:44:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是魔苟斯的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are a friend of Morgoth's.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.50,0:44:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年魔苟斯被打败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When Morgoth was defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.62,0:45:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像一个攥紧的大拳头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was as if a great, clenched fist
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.79,0:45:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我的脖子上松开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}had released its grasp from my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.04,0:45:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第一个日出的寂静之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the stillness of that first sunrise,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.75,0:45:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于又感受到了独一之神的光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at last, I felt the light of The One again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.62,0:45:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道如果我想得到宽恕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I knew if ever I was to be forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.20,0:45:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须治愈 我曾助纣为虐破坏掉的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I had to heal everything that I had helped ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.79,0:45:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何补赎都无法抹去你犯下的恶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No penance could ever erase the evil you have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.54,0:45:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你根本不是这样想的 -我的想法用不着你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-That is not what you believe. -Do not tell me what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.83,0:45:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. You told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.50,0:45:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们胜利之后 你说我不必再纠结以前做过的任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After our victory, you said that whatever I'd done before I could be free of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.45,0:45:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是你骗我在先 -我告诉了你真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You deceived me. -I told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.91,0:45:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你我做过恶 是你不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you that I had done evil, and you did not care.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.58,0:45:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你知道 跟我们的未来相比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you knew that our past meant nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.04,0:45:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的过去毫无意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}weighed against our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.62,0:45:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有这样的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no such future.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.91,0:45:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.29,0:46:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都用怀疑的眼光看待你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All others look on you with doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.87,0:46:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有我能看到你的伟大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I alone can see your greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.45,0:46:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能看到你的光芒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I alone can see your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.50,0:46:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会让我变成暴君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would make me a tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.00,0:46:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你成为女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would make you a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.04,0:46:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像大海和太阳一样美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fair as the sea and the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.87,0:46:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比大地的根基还要坚固\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stronger than the foundations of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.25,0:46:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你 国王大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you. My king.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.70,0:46:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗魔君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.87,0:46:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Not dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.95,0:46:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你在我身边 就不会是黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not with you at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.95,0:47:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经告诉我 命运有意把我们安排在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me once, that we were brought together for a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.29,0:47:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.54,0:47:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赠我以光芒 我赐你以力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bind me to the light. And I bind you to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.62,0:47:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以一起拯救中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together, we can save this Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Save?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.04,0:47:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是统治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.66,0:47:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这二者没什么区别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.45,0:47:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么… 我永远不会站在你那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that is why... I will never be at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.58,0:47:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.20,0:47:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我 你们精灵将会衰落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without me, your people will fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.37,0:47:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑影将会蔓延 加重 直至笼罩整个世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the shadow will spread and darken to cover all the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.66,0:47:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你需要我 -我当初就应该把你丢在海上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You need me. -I should have left you on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.33,0:47:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当时在海里 就是因为精灵们把你赶了出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A sea you were on because the Elves cast you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.87,0:47:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把你赶走 就因为你乞求他们给你几个士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They cast you out for deigning to beg them for a few petty soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.37,0:47:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你告诉他们 你是我的盟友时 他们会怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What will they do when you tell them that you were my ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.95,0:48:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你告诉他们是你救活了索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you tell them that Sauron lives because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.62,0:48:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you will die because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.66,0:48:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.16,0:48:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deceiver!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.04,0:48:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 住手  埃尔隆德 是埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Galadriel, stop! Elrond. It's Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.45,0:48:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.75,0:49:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们第一次见面是在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did we first meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.70,0:49:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海滨 当时我刚成为孤儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seaside. When I was first orphaned.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.79,0:49:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我独自一人 是个年幼的 半精灵男孩 举目无亲 也没有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was alone. A young, half-elven boy, without friend or kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.62,0:49:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave me water.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.66,0:49:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃尔隆德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elrond.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.75,0:49:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}á cuith tess?, Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.29,0:49:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯勒布林博在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Celebrimbor. Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.29,0:49:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作间 他马上就要完工了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Workshop. He'll almost be finished by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.75,0:49:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.08,0:49:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel! Galadriel! What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.54,0:49:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.08,0:49:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Is it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.79,0:49:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 你浑身湿透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel. You're as wet as a river rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.50,0:49:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.66,0:49:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我刚把她 从格蓝都因河中拖了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I pulled her from the waters of Glanduin.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.66,0:49:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蓝都因河 怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Glanduin? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.70,0:50:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.25,0:50:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔布兰德去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Halbrand?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.20,0:50:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他走了 我怀疑他不会回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is gone. And I doubt he will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.04,0:50:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他再回来 谁都不准再与他联络\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And should he ever, none of us are to treat with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.33,0:50:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条溪流旁发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened by that stream?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.50,0:50:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前跟我说你犯过一个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You spoke to me once of a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.79,0:50:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你不会再犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One you said you would not make again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.12,0:50:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你让我这个承诺很难兑现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're making that promise very difficult to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.83,0:50:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是容易办到的话 也就不需要信任了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were it easy, it would not require trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.37,0:50:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们继续吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, do we proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.37,0:50:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.95,0:50:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须做三个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must make three.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.04,0:50:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个 为什么要三个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three? Why three?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.79,0:50:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单个容易堕落 成双总会分裂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One will always corrupt. Two will divide.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.75,0:50:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而三个 就有了平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But with three, there is balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.37,0:51:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天锻造的力量必须只属于精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The powers we forge today must be for the Elves alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.41,0:51:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得被他人触及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Untouched by other hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.66,0:51:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞尔 我已经确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel, I have determined that the purity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.62,0:51:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合金中次要矿石的纯度至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the lesser ores in the alloy is crucial.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.25,0:51:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要最精纯的金银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need gold and silver of the most exquisite quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.79,0:51:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要维林诺的金银\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need gold and silver from Valinor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.45,0:51:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的创造需要…牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True creation requires... sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.08,0:51:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得其他什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you remember anything more yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.29,0:51:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一些碎片的印象了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fragments. Impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.33,0:52:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想起来的越来越多 但为了找到 余下的记忆 我必须前往鲁恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More has come. But to discover the rest, I know I must go to Rh?n.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.62,0:52:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把你的名字都搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They were wrong about your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.87,0:52:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们把地名 也弄错了呢 或者撒谎了 或者…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if they're wrong about that, too? Or lying, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.45,0:52:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他们说的是真的 但我无法解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What they said, I knew to be true with a... a certainty that I can't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.29,0:52:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.33,0:52:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们称呼你为“伊斯塔尔”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They called you something else. "Istar."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.08,0:52:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的种族吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that your kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.54,0:52:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“伊斯塔尔”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Istar?"
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.08,0:52:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们的语言中 意思是“智者”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In your tongue, that means "wise one."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.41,0:52:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.45,0:52:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“巫师”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Wizard."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.41,0:52:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不和我们一起走吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're really not coming with us, are ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.62,0:53:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时 我们的前路 早已被更强大的力量所安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Betimes, our paths are laid before us by powers greater than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.75,0:53:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时 我们的任务就是要百折不挠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In those moments, it's our task to make our feet go
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.70,0:53:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚决踏上心里所忌惮的那条道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where our hearts wish not to tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.04,0:53:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论沿途有什么危险在等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter the perils awaiting us on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.87,0:53:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来有点像冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Sounds a bit like an adventure. -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.58,0:53:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一个人而言 只是旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alone, it's just a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.58,0:53:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一群人而言 才是冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now adventures, they must be shared.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.70,0:53:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我冒过的险 比任何毛脚族能想到的还要多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think I've had about as much adventure as any Harfoot could ever hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.75,0:53:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里写道 如果往北走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Says here, if we go north-ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.16,0:53:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路上我们会有三十天都很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have thirty days of clear trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.79,0:53:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是新鲜草地 没有食人妖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All fresh grass and no trolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.95,0:54:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嘿 看起来好像都是下坡… -你拿倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey, hey, hey! -All downhill, look like... -You're holding it upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.70,0:54:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 玛尔娃 我们要连续数周爬坡过坎披荆斩棘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Malva. Nothing but steep slopes and brickle-brambles for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.58,0:54:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你这么聪明 怎么不去探路呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if you're so quick and wise, why don't you do the trail-finding?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.08,0:54:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加留意小孩和掉队者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch out for little ones and stragglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.25,0:54:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人偏离路线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody goes off-trail!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.91,0:54:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有人独自前行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nobody walks alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.83,0:54:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是从萨道克的嘴里 说出来更好听一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounded better when Sadoc said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.12,0:54:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望那个糟老头子还和我们在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wish the old goat were still with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.70,0:54:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他与我们同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.41,0:54:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.62,0:54:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在有更重要的事情要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a part of something bigger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.20,0:55:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He needs ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.58,0:55:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你属于外面的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you belong out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.41,0:55:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good-bye, Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.87,0:55:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-再见… -要小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Good-bye... -Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.62,0:55:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.95,0:55:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你带灯了吗  -当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Did you pack your lantern? -Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.29,0:55:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.41,0:55:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧…再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.87,0:55:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nori...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.45,0:55:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这是给那个大家伙吃的蜗牛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. Here's snails for the big fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.87,0:55:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道他胃口有多大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know how hungry he gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.83,0:56:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多带一条毯子 以防感冒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And an extra blanket in case you get cold. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.75,0:56:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们看看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.16,0:56:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不是个好爹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some father.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要踏入外面的世界了 而我却什么都没有教过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you're heading into the big beyond and I haven't taught you a bloomin' thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.29,0:56:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 您当然教过我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. Hey. Sure you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.25,0:56:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情一定要上好双保险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always quench your fire with water and earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.45,0:56:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在河流旁上厕所 免得到下游的时候想喝水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't squat by a river. Never know when you'll need a drink downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.62,0:56:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有礼貌的毛脚族才有可能更快地成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And a Harfoot without manners is as like to get far in life as a square wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.91,0:56:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则寸步难行…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Square wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.04,0:56:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 您说的这些我都认真听了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was listening to all of it, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.25,0:57:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探索河水能流多远 去了解麻雀是在哪里学的春天之歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find where the river runs. Where the sparrows learn their songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.50,0:57:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.62,0:57:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我会多加小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.62,0:57:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.25,0:57:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会勇敢而无畏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.41,0:57:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, go on. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.79,0:57:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁你还有这份勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on. Before you lose your nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.25,0:57:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说趁我们还有勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or we lose ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.25,0:58:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 诺瑞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait! Nori!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.41,0:58:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.45,0:58:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我最爱的人总是要离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why does everyone I love the most always have to go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.91,0:58:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不这样做 我们就永远学不到新东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause I think if we didn't, then we'd never learn anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.25,0:58:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会回来吗 你保证吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll come back? Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.00,0:58:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你保证会照顾好大家吗  -当然了 蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You promise to look after everyone? -Course I will, ankle-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.29,0:58:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我在这广阔 而狂野的世界里最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're my best friend in this whole wide, wild world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.95,0:58:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意为你做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd do anything for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.37,0:59:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界没那么大 波比 只不过是我们非常小而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The world's not that wide, Poppy. It's just that we're so bleedin' small.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.45,0:59:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟紧那个高个子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stick close to that tall fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.00,0:59:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个患难与共的好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a good friend in a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.08,0:59:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但远不及你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not so good as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.95,0:59:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你确定吗  -无比确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Are you certain? -More than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.00,0:59:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 他们都在向你挥手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, they're all waving at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.79,0:59:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我转身 我就永远都走不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I turn around, I won't ever be able to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.41,1:00:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那你在前边带头可能会好一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then perhaps it would be best if you lead off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.50,1:00:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真到该走的时候 却感觉脚如注铅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, now that it comes to it, my feet feel heavy as iron.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.54,1:00:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用说 我根本不知道前路在何方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to mention, I haven't an inkling which way to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.00,1:00:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.91,1:00:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.20,1:00:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not entirely.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.54,1:00:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边飘来的空气有一股香甜味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a sweet smell on the air this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.08,1:00:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你怀疑的时候 埃拉诺白兰地足…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When in doubt, Elanor Brandyfoot...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.62,1:00:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远跟着嗅觉走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}always follow your nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.12,1:07:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹苍下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three rings for the Elven-kings
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.58,1:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵众王得其三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Under the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.00,1:07:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石殿中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven for the Dwarf-lords
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.37,1:07:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮人诸侯得其七\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In their halls of stone
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.66,1:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尘世间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nine for Mortal Men
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.20,1:07:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必死凡人得其九\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doomed to die
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.54,1:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔多翳影 王座乌沉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One for the Dark Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.87,1:07:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗魔君执其尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On his dark throne
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.16,1:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔多翳影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the Land of Mordor
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.91,1:08:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪暗深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the Shadows lie
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.62,1:08:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪暗深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the Shadows lie
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.33,1:08:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统御余众 魔戒至尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Ring to rule them all
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.08,1:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网罗余众 魔戒至尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Ring to find them
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.08,1:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁锢余众 魔戒至尊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Ring to bring them all
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.25,1:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁锢众戒黑暗中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the darkness Bind them
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.25,1:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔多大地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the Land of Mordor
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.41,1:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑影幢幢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the Shadows lie...
